# AINEX Project Modular File Organization

This document organizes all files in the AINEX project into logical modules based on their functionality and purpose.

## 1. Core Application & Configuration
- next.config.js - Next.js configuration
- next-env.d.ts - Next.js TypeScript definitions
- package.json - Node.js dependencies and scripts
- package-lock.json - Dependency lock file
- package-monitor.json - Monitoring package config
- package.json.backup - Backup package config
- tsconfig.json - TypeScript configuration
- tsconfig.tsbuildinfo - TypeScript build info
- types.ts - Global type definitions
- constants.ts - Application constants
- .eslintrc.json - ESLint configuration
- eslint.config.mjs - ESLint config (modern)
- tailwind.config.ts - Tailwind CSS configuration
- postcss.config.js - PostCSS configuration
- vercel.json - Vercel deployment config

